      "There is no existing message broker or CDC infrastructure in place",
      "The shared database does not use PostgreSQL Row-Level Security or role-based access controls currently",
      "The cron job triggering refunds does not implement idempotency checks externally",
      "The system serves enough traffic that synchronous Notification coupling is causing measurable incidents"
    ]
  }
